data.description: Are you searching for an affordable condo for yourself? This gorgeous ground floor 2-bedroom 2-bathroom condo is what you have been searching for. This unit features an oversized primary bedroom that has its own sitting area and bathroom. The dining room and spacious living room area is the perfect space to entertain your guests or just relax after a long day. It is a fairly flat easy walk from the parking area straight to your front door. Each condo comes with an easily accessible designated storage unit. Seller is willing to offer seller concessions. Eligible for Conventional and VA financing.
